ss. She is known for her roles as Yalena \"Dutch\" Yardeen in Killjoys (2015–2019), Ornela in Game of Thrones (2016), F\'Nale Zandor in Ready Player One (2018), Ava Starr / Ghost in the MCU film Ant-Man and the Wasp (2018), and the title character in The Stranger (2020).\n\nShe began her career in 2011, providing voice work for the video game Dark Souls. She went on to make appearances in episodes of television series Misfits (2011), Black Mirror (2016), Whitechapel (2012), The Syndicate (2012), The Midnight Beast (2012), and The Hour (2012). From 2012 to 2013, she took the lead role of Viva in the Spice Girls-themed West End musical Viva Forever!\n\nIn 2015, she had a starring role in the SyFy series Killjoys. In 2016, she had a guest-star role on the HBO series Game of Thrones. That year, she appeared in the Black Mirror episode \"Playtest\" and an episode of \"The Tunnel\". In 2018, she starred in Ready Player One and Ant-Man and the Wasp.\n\nDescription above is from the Wikipedia article Hannah John-Kamen, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.'),(14572,4860,'fr-FR','Hannah John-Kamen',''),(14573,4860,'zh-TW','Hannah John-Kamen',''),(14574,4861,'en-US','Robbie Amell','Robbie Amell (born April 21, 1988) is a Canadian actor, who is best known for his roles in Resident Evil: Welcome to Raccoon City, True Jackson, VP and Picture This as well as Fred Jones in Scooby-Doo! The Mystery Begins and Scooby-Doo! Curse of the Lake Monster.'),(14575,4861,'fr-FR','Robbie Amell',''),(14576,4861,'zh-TW','Robbie Amell',''),(14577,4862,'en-US','Tom Hopper','Tom Hopper (born 28 January 1985 in Coalville, Leicestershire) is an English actor who has appeared in several television programmes and films including Merlin, Doctor Who, Casualty and Tormented.'),(14578,4862,'fr-FR','Tom Hopper',''),(14579,4862,'zh-TW','Tom Hopper',''),(14580,4863,'en-US','Avan Jogia','Avan Jogia (born February 9, 1992) is a Canadian actor and singer best known for playing Beck Oliver on Victorious\'Although he is from Vancouver, he spends most of his time between Vancouver and Los Angeles.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Avan Jogia, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.'),(14581,4863,'fr-FR','Avan Jogia',''),(14582,4863,'zh-TW','Avan Jogia',''),(14583,4864,'en-US','Donal Logue','Donal Francis Logue (born February 27, 1966) is an Irish-Canadian film and television actor, producer and writer. His notable roles include starring in the film The Tao of Steve, Sons of Anarchy, Vikings, the sitcom Grounded for Life, the television series Copper and the detective series Terriers. He stared as detective Harvey Bullock in Fox\'s Gotham and had a recurring role in NBC\'s Law & Order: Special Victims Unit as Lt. Declan Murphy.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Donal Logue, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.'),(14584,4864,'fr-FR','Donal Logue',''),(14585,4864,'zh-TW','Donal Logue',''),(14586,4865,'en-US','Neal McDonough','Neal McDonough was trained at the London Academy of Dramatic Arts and Sciences. His theatre credits include \'Cheap Talk\', \'Foreigner\', \'As You Like It\', \'Rivals\', \'A Midsummer Night\'s Dream\', \'Bald Soprano\', and \'Waiting for Lefty\'. The young actor won a 1991 Best Actor Dramalogue Award for \'Away Alone\'. McDonough has been a \'Star Trek\' fan since he was a kid. Playing Lieutenant Hawk in \'Star Trek First Contact\' was a life-long dream. McDonough has three pictures on his bedroom wall. One is a picture of his mom, the other is the Holy Virgin Mary, and the third is William Shatner as Captain Kirk. He has numerous television credits including \'NYPD Blue\', \'Quantum Leap\', and the voice of Bruce Banner in the animated series \'The Incredible Hulk\' among others. He graduated Syracuse University with a Bachelor of Fine Arts degree in 1988. '),(14587,4865,'fr-FR','Neal McDonough',''),(14588,4865,'zh-TW','Neal McDonough','尼爾·麥克唐納（英語：Neal McDonough，1966年2月13日－）美國知名男演員。\n\n1966年，麥克唐納出生在美國麻薩諸塞州波士頓，母親凱薩琳，父親弗蘭克·麥克唐納，他們都是愛爾蘭移民，信奉羅馬天主教。麥克唐納畢業於雪城大學和倫敦音樂與戲劇藝術學院。\n\n2003年，麥克唐納和瑞文·羅伯遜結婚，兩人育有5個孩子。'),(14589,4866,'en-US','Lily Gao','Lily Gao is a first-generation Chinese-Canadian actor, model, and painter.'),(14590,4866,'fr-FR','Lily Gao',''),(14591,4866,'zh-TW','Lily Gao',''),(14592,4867,'en-US','Chad Rook',''),(14593,4867,'fr-FR','Chad Rook',''),(14594,4867,'zh-TW','Chad Rook',''),(14595,4868,'en-US','Marina Mazepa',''),(14596,4868,'fr-FR','Marina Mazepa',''),(14597,4868,'zh-TW','Marina Mazepa',''),(14598,4869,'en-US','Paul W. S. Anderson','Paul William Scott Anderson (born 4 March 1965), also known as Paul WS Anderson or Paul Anderson, is an English film director who regularly works in science fiction movies and video game adaptations.'),(14599,4869,'fr-FR','Paul W. S. Anderson',''),(14600,4869,'zh-TW','Paul W. S. Anderson',''),(14601,4870,'en-US','Jeremy Bolt',''),(14602,4870,'fr-FR','Jeremy Bolt',''),(14603,4870,'zh-TW','Jeremy Bolt',''),(14604,4871,'en-US','Robert Kulzer',''),(14605,4871,'fr-FR','Robert Kulzer',''),(14606,4871,'zh-TW','Robert Kulzer',''),(14607,4872,'en-US','Vincent Rother',''),(14608,4872,'fr-FR','Vincent Rother',''),(14609,4872,'zh-TW','Vincent Rother',''),(14613,4874,'en-US','Martin Moszkowicz',''),(14614,4874,'fr-FR','Martin Moszkowicz',''),(14615,4874,'zh-TW','Martin Moszkowicz',''),(14616,4875,'en-US','Maxime Alexandre','Maxime Alexandre is a Belgian Cinematographer'),(14617,4875,'fr-FR','Maxime Alexandre',''),(14618,4875,'zh-TW','Maxime Alexandre',''),(14619,4876,'en-US','Victor Hadida',''),(14620,4876,'fr-FR','Victor Hadida',''),(14621,4876,'zh-TW','Victor Hadida',''),(14622,4877,'en-US','Scott Strauss',''),(14623,4877,'fr-FR','Scott Strauss',''),(14624,4877,'zh-TW','Scott Strauss',''),(14625,4878,'en-US','Mike Chute','Mike Chute is a Canadian stunt performer and coordinator.'),(14626,4878,'fr-FR','Mike Chute',''),(14627,4878,'zh-TW','Mike Chute',''),(14628,4879,'en-US','Keslee 